statements: SELECT * FROM website_traffic_data WHERE id = 1;
SELECT page_url, date_visited FROM website_traffic_data WHERE time_spent_on_page > 60;
SELECT id, page_url, time_spent_on_page FROM website_traffic_data WHERE user_agent LIKE '%Chrome%';
SELECT id, date_visited, referrer_url FROM website_traffic_data WHERE date_visited BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-01-31';
SELECT * FROM website_traffic_data WHERE time_spent_on_page < 30 ORDER BY date_visited DESC;
SELECT * FROM website_traffic_data ORDER BY date_visited DESC, time_spent_on_page ASC LIMIT 10
SELECT page_url, COUNT(*) AS visits FROM website_traffic_data GROUP BY page_url ORDER BY visits DESC LIMIT 5
SELECT DISTINCT referrer_url FROM website_traffic_data WHERE date_visited BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-01-31'
SELECT page_url, user_agent FROM website_traffic_data WHERE user_agent LIKE '%Chrome%' AND time_spent_on_page > 60
SELECT AVG(time_spent_on_page) AS avg_time_spent FROM website_traffic_data
SELECT * FROM website_traffic_data LIMIT 10;
SELECT visit_date, page_url, visitor_id FROM website_traffic_data WHERE visit_duration > 60;
SELECT visitor_id, visit_date, page_url FROM website_traffic_data ORDER BY visit_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM marketing_performance_data WHERE impressions > 500 AND clicks > 100;
SELECT SUM(clicks) AS total_clicks, AVG(impressions) AS avg_impressions FROM marketing_performance_data;
SELECT * FROM website_traffic_data WHERE visit_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT page_url, visit_date, visit_duration FROM website_traffic_data ORDER BY visit_duration DESC;
SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_visitors FROM website_traffic_data WHERE visitor_id = 1001;
SELECT AVG(visit_duration) AS avg_duration FROM website_traffic_data;

SELECT marketing_performance_data.campaign_id, SUM(clicks) AS total_clicks FROM marketing_performance_data JOIN website_traffic_data ON marketing_performance_data.website_traffic_id = website_traffic_data.id GROUP BY marketing_performance_data.campaign_id ORDER BY total_clicks DESC;
SELECT * FROM traffic_data ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT page_url, visitor_id FROM traffic_data WHERE visitor_id = 123;
SELECT query_text FROM search_queries WHERE timestamp > '2022-01-01';
SELECT page_url, error_code FROM website_performance WHERE error_code IS NOT NULL;
SELECT id, page_url, timestamp FROM traffic_data WHERE page_url LIKE '%example.com%';
SELECT page_url, visitor_id, timestamp FROM traffic_data WHERE visitor_id = 123 ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT query_text, page_url, timestamp FROM search_queries WHERE page_url LIKE '%example.com%' ORDER BY timestamp ASC;
SELECT page_url, load_time, error_code FROM website_performance WHERE error_code IS NOT NULL ORDER BY load_time DESC;
SELECT * FROM traffic_data JOIN search_queries ON traffic_data.page_url = search_queries.page_url WHERE traffic_data.timestamp > '2022-01-01';

SELECT website_performance.page_url, website_performance.load_time, traffic_data.visitor_id FROM website_performance INNER JOIN traffic_data ON website_performance.page_url = traffic_data.page_url WHERE traffic_data.visitor_id = 456 ORDER BY website_performance.load_time ASC;
SELECT * FROM website_visits;
SELECT visitor_name, visitor_email FROM visitors ORDER BY visitor_name DESC;
SELECT page_title, page_url FROM pages WHERE page_category = 'Blog' LIMIT 10;
SELECT visit_timestamp, page_id FROM website_visits WHERE visitor_id = 100 ORDER BY visit_timestamp ASC;
SELECT source_name, source_type FROM traffic_sources WHERE source_type IS NOT NULL;
SELECT * FROM website_visits WHERE visit_timestamp > '2022-01-01';
SELECT visitor_name, visitor_email FROM visitors ORDER BY visitor_name DESC;
SELECT page_url, page_title, page_category FROM pages WHERE page_category='News' ORDER BY page_title ASC;
SELECT visitor_name, visit_timestamp FROM visitors JOIN website_visits ON visitors.visitor_id = website_visits.visitor_id WHERE visitor_name LIKE 'A%' ORDER BY visit_timestamp DESC;

SELECT visitor_name, page_url, source_name FROM visitors JOIN website_visits ON visitors.visitor_id = website_visits.visitor_id JOIN traffic_sources ON website_visits.page_id = traffic_sources.source_id ORDER BY visitor_name ASC, page_url DESC;
SELECT * FROM website_visits ORDER BY visit_date DESC, visit_id ASC LIMIT 10;
SELECT visit_id, visit_date, visitor_ip FROM website_visits WHERE page_url LIKE '%example.com%';
SELECT referrer_url, COUNT(*) AS referral_count FROM website_visits GROUP BY referrer_url HAVING COUNT(*) > 5;
SELECT site_url, site_description FROM referrer_sites WHERE site_category = 'Social Media' ORDER BY site_url ASC;
SELECT query_text, search_time, search_results_count FROM search_queries ORDER BY search_time DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT visit_id, visit_date, page_url FROM website_visits;
SELECT click_id, click_time, click_source FROM click_rates WHERE click_source = 'Organic' ORDER BY click_time DESC;
SELECT query_text, search_time, search_results_count FROM search_queries WHERE search_location = 'US' LIMIT 10;
SELECT site_url, site_description FROM referrer_sites WHERE site_category = 'Social Media' ORDER BY site_description ASC;
SELECT page_url, load_time_ms, status_code FROM website_performance WHERE load_time_ms > 1000 AND status_code = 404 ORDER BY load_time_ms DESC;
